The 7-week calculation is correct because it properly accounts for Steve's weekly reading pattern. He reads 100 pages on three days per week, making his weekly total:<tool_call>
{
    "name": math_eval,
    "arguments": {"expr": "100 * 3"}
}
</tool_call>
<tool_result>
